Edie McClurg https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edie_McClurg 0 Edie McClurg (born July 23, 1951) is an American stand-up comedian, actress, singer and voice actress. She has performed in nearly 90 films and 55 television episodes, often portraying characters with a cheery Midwestern accent.
